<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> koṉeriṉmai koṇṭāṉ vaṭaparicāra nāṭṭil Uṭaiyār tirumurukaṉpūṇṭi
<lb n="2"/>Uṭaiyār tirumurukaṉpūṇṭiyāḷuṭaiya nāyaṉārkku tirumaṭaippaḷḷip puṟamāka nāṅ kuṭuttavūr viracoḻa vaḷanāṭṭil tirup <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>ṉāṉkellaikkuṭpaṭṭa ṉaṉcey puṉcey māṉpaṭukāṭu teṉpaṭuvarai mīṉpaṭu cuṉai poṉpaṭukuṭṭam Ivvūrāl varu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>num palaviḷakkup piccaṉuḷḷiṭṭārkkum maṉṟāṭṭu Oṉṟum Aṉupavittup potuvārkaḷākavum Ivvūrkku veṇṭuṅ kuṭiyu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>nantamar Eppeṟpaṭṭārum pāṟpaṭuttuk kuṭukka Itu māṟṟuvāṉ vaḻi Ēḻeccamaṟuvāṉ Itu paṉmā<hi rend="grantha">heśvara rakṣai <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation">.</g></hi>
</p>

